{"tid":354717,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加預言英超快將有女領隊","createTime":"2017-08-10T16:28:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T04:49:38.000Z","uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"18825c5b07e17be1f80f52ce3e156c9072aa6a75","tid":354717,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T16:28:23.000Z","msg":"職業足球一定是男人天下？香港的陳婉婷早用行動否定了這個看法。而阿仙奴主帥雲格亦相信隨著球隊管理日漸科學化，未來帶領球隊出戰的可能是管理專才多於足球通，並預言英超短時間內將出現女領隊。<br />\n<br />\n雲格出席一個活動時談及未來球會的營運方向，並指女領隊將於不久將來出現在英超：「我個人深信短期內英超將有女領隊出現。相信未來10至15年內，帶領球隊出賽的將是管理專才而非精通足球的專家。因為未來一支球隊將有很多科學家負責分析，而帶領他們出賽的將是善於行政管理的精英，因為所有決定都是建基於技術分析。」"},{"pid":"c2f3663decb50fc687946e7a90b41bd60f893eed","tid":354717,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T16:30:25.000Z","msg":"牛丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02cf16b2532f1f33cc85b7a95a2f506070ae9ab9","tid":354717,"uid":1166,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T16:36:11.000Z","msg":"新任阿狗領隊<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170809/photo/0809-00176-009b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170809%2Fphoto%2F0809-00176-009b1.jpg&h=d688b282&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58944bd8d4b0c4fd7dc0ea73e504c7336ad72b82","tid":354717,"uid":17081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T16:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.balls.ie/uploads/2013/10/Guitar.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.balls.ie%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F10%2FGuitar.gif&h=70cf4f09&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1810adc841a89b7b1a71beb43a953624217e97f","tid":354717,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T17:03:28.000Z","msg":"eva<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f0c7020bb1395c54d7bafaed05fd2d4659c1746","tid":354717,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl